data.oai_dc:dc: Dung breeding insects and Dung eprinomectin

Two spreadsheets are present in this file - one with emerged insect data and the second with dung eprinomectin concentrations. Insect data are organized by week of dung sample collection (column) and taxa of emerged insects (row). Eprinomectin data are similarly organized but rows contain eprinomectin concentrations expressed on dung fresh weight or dry weight basis.
